entry.title: Portland, Ore., Is Losing Residents Weary of Crime and High Housing Prices
entry.content: The city’s population decline of about 17,400 people to 635,000 was the sixth largest decline among the 50 largest U.S. cities.

entry.title: Putin Moves to Seize Control of Wagner's Global Empire
entry.content: The Kremlin assured nations in Africa and the Middle East that it would manage Wagner forces, which have spread Russian power at little cost to Putin.

entry.title: Wagner Chief Prigozhin Planned to Capture Russian Military Leaders
entry.content: The mercenary leader planned to capture Russia’s military leadership as part of the mutiny, Western officials said, and he accelerated his plans after the domestic intelligence agency became aware of the plot.
